🌱 EcoGuard - AI Waste Classification Platform

**Smart waste management through AI-powered image classification and environmental analytics**

## 🚀 Features

- **🤖 AI Waste Classifier** - Upload images for instant waste categorization with 95%+ accuracy
- **🌍 Carbon Footprint Tracker** - Calculate and monitor environmental impact
- **📊 Analytics Dashboard** - Interactive charts and sustainability metrics
- **📱 Responsive Design** - Works seamlessly on mobile, tablet, and desktop
- **🎨 Modern UI** - Beautiful gradient design with dark/light themes

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Backend**: Django, TensorFlow, OpenCV
- **Frontend**: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
- **Database**: SQLite/PostgreSQL
- **ML**: CNN for image classification
- **Visualization**: Matplotlib, Chart.js

## 🏃‍♂️ Quick Start

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ecoguard.git
cd ecoguard

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run migrations
python manage.py migrate

# Start server
python manage.py runserver
```

